01/24/83  Control Arguments

Two lists of approved standard control arguments follow.  The first
contains general purpose control arguments used by several system
commands.  Programmers should use these control arguments whenever
possible.  The second list consists of more specialized control
arguments, which cover a more limited range of situations.


